<p>On Dropdown click, Boostrap immediately closes all menus with `Dropdown.clearMenus()` preventing submenus by default because the parent menus will hide as a result.</p>
<p>For this to work, we will need to patch Bootstrap's Dropdown.toggle method with the following snippet</p>
<p class="alert alert-danger"> Third Tier Sub Menus do not work with this code</p>

<pre>
